{"tid":2116867,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"FIFA取消今年世界足球先生評選","createTime":"2020-07-20T12:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T12:44:11.000Z","uid":147522,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cb5acc22832589433151df222ce5829da6404d21","tid":2116867,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:20:11.000Z","msg":"據西班牙媒體報導，受到新冠病毒的影響，國際足協決定取消今年的世界足球先生評選。<br />\n<br />\n　　《馬卡報》報導，頒獎典禮原定於今年9月在米蘭進行，但由於新冠病毒疫情仍然嚴重，今年的頒獎典禮不會舉行，美斯（Lionel Messi）和C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）都無法在這個球壇至高獎項上一較高低。在去年的評選中，美斯成功當選。<br />\n<br />\n　　目前，大多數聯賽仍在暫停中，歐國盃已經被推遲到明年，在這樣的情況下，國際足協決定取消今年的世界足球先生評選，國際足協主席恩芬天奴（Gianni Infantino）認為這個時候進行大規模的頒獎也是不正確的。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n　　同時，《馬卡報》指出，金球獎的評比如何處理仍是未知數，金球獎自1956年以來每年都舉行頒獎典禮。"},{"pid":"57fc1ea6217e43c649752945798255a852824c98","tid":2116867,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"迫害美斯"},{"pid":"620068953b5865979bd9b24c6bb56e332f3baadb","tid":2116867,"uid":49015,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"57fc1ea6217e43c649752945798255a852824c98","tid":2116867,"uid":133100,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:33:26.000Z","msg":"迫害美斯"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:36:01.000Z","msg":"雙20牙"},{"pid":"ff42a96ec600d39d34655a65e09854b61c7f3f8a","tid":2116867,"uid":308020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:36:26.000Z","msg":"又迫害我朗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aad31e604b5d1d3966d9fc97b0a429d773152b4e","tid":2116867,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"迫害利雲"},{"pid":"f19288c1e3b16b818bfcd6a7c2dd4a20ea5b6a07","tid":2116867,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T12:41:22.000Z","msg":"迫害尼馬"},{"pid":"86cd3dcb4177671d313eeb2c63636fa5c7669c0a","tid":2116867,"uid":282509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f19288c1e3b16b818bf